<li>$|e^z| = e^x,Arg(e^z) = y+2k\pi$</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>对数函数：$Lnz =ln|r|+iArgz$
<ol>
<li>函数在除去原点和负实轴的$z$平面内解析，且$(Lnz)' = \frac{1}{z}$</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>三角函数
<ol>
<li>$cosz = \frac{e^{iz}+e^{-iz}}{2},sinz = \frac{e^{iz}-e^{-iz}}{2i}$</li>
<li>$chz = \frac{e^z+e^{-z}}{2},shz = \frac{e^z-e^{-z}}{2}$</li>
